\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 The number of note symbols available depends on the number of lines in the staff, which can be set to any practical number (most tablature staves have 4, 5, or 6 lines).  Tablature chords may be beamed (see the \b Beam\b0  \b Tool\b0 ), as shown in this example:\par
